00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:03,679
Leave some men behind

2
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:04,599
to kill them.

3
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,799
The rest of you, follow me!

4
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:07,959
Keep chasing!

5
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,560
Yes, sir.

6
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:10,640
Kill them!

7
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:50,400
You need to get out of here, now.

8
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,599
You're not the one they're after.

9
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,519
I'm getting paid for this.

10
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,159
You barely make anything a month.

11
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,439
Why risk your life?

12
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,760
But my salary is five times yours.

13
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,479
Gu Changkong.

14
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,240
We're old classmates, after all.

15
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,199
How about you let us go?

16
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,479
If you don't die,

17
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:21,919
how do I justify attacking Shanhai City?

18
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:25,400
So you're saying

19
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,960
this hurdle

20
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,639
we're not getting past today, huh?

21
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,560
Tell you what.

22
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,039
Cooperate with me,

23
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,199
and I promise your death will be less painful.

24
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,000
How's that sound?

25
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,599
Why waste breath on them?

26
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:38,560
Just attack!

27
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,560
Hurry up and leave, now!

28
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,360
Go!

29
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,039
No.

30
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,439
We die together!

31
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,919
If you come over, I'll just die faster!

32
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,199
Zhu Rong!

33
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,039
Flames!

34
00:03:58,639 --> 00:03:59,360
Are you okay?

35
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,199
Liu Chengfeng.

36
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,520
Hiding behind a woman now, are you?

37
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,479
She's quite the catch.

38
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,159
Once you're dead,

39
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,919
I'll gladly take her off your hands.

40
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,720
At a time like this,

41
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,519
cut the lovey-dovey stuff.

42
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,519
So devoted.

43
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,560
I'm touched.

44
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,120
Let's see what you can do now.

45
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,959
Kill him!

46
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:48,279
She looks badly hurt.

47
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,519
Does she need a doctor?

48
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,639
What's the situation?

49
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:01,040
Qiu Ge died in battle.

50
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:02,959
The others are trapped.

51
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,680
Status unknown.

52
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,439
We're the champions.

53
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:21,839
We only took back what was ours.

54
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:24,959
Why did it have to cost two lives?

55
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,160
We want to leave the Imperial Capital.

56
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,480
Are we wrong?

57
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,879
We listened to Little Cleaner.

58
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,480
No killing or setting fires,

59
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,920
no causing trouble.

60
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,680
And in the end,

61
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,279
what did we get?

62
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,240
So

63
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:46,240
if I kill every single one of you here,

64
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,360
I wouldn't be wrong either.

65
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,120
Watch over Little Cleaner.

66
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:05,680
Today,

67
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,319
I can finally stop being reasonable.

68
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,079
What are you standing around for?

69
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:10,959
Get him!

70
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,199
Whoever kills him

71
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,439
gets ten million!

72
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,279
Next,

73
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:51,680
it's your turn.

74
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:52,720
You're awake.

75
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:53,879
Idiot.

76
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,519
Still breathing, you damn cripple?

77
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,639
My clothes are ripped.

78
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,160
Tongtong bought them for me.

79
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,279
I want to see Tongtong.

80
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,959
What a bitch.

81
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:12,000
What do we do with them now?

82
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,560
Hang their corpses at the Black Street entrance.

83
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:19,680
Three years...

84
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,480
Did you forget about the fool?

85
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,199
Tell me,

86
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,199
a guy who can't even count

87
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,279
actually knows how to use a smartphone,

88
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:39,079
to take notes and record videos.

89
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,680
The little bit of brainpower he has,

90
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,360
he used it all on Tongtong.

91
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,000
Is he really a fool, or just faking it?

92
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,959
Kill them now?

93
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,439
I'm worried Tongtong might wake up.

94
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:52,439
I mean them.

95
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,879
Now that you're all back,

96
00:07:58,199 --> 00:08:00,079
there probably won't be enough room in the carriage.

97
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,480
And if we haul their corpses

98
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,839
back to Black Street,

99
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:04,480
they'll have started to stink.

100
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,720
How about this.

101
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:10,079
Let's come back in a freezer truck next time to kill them.

102
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,879
Works for me.

103
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,399
We'll have to come back again anyway.

104
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:27,040
Aren't you celebrating a bit too soon?

105
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:28,360
You think you can get away?

106
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,840
Father.

107
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,399
Why are you here?

108
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,679
If you're here,

109
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,440
it means I lost at the Elder Council.

110
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,679
I refuse to accept it!

111
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:44,120
I still have a chance to bounce back! I—

112
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,039
The moment this old Taoist showed up,

113
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,960
even the sky changed.

114
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,639
He's got some tricks.

115
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,159
Su Yang!

116
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,720
Go crazy on him again!

117
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,279
Bro,

118
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,799
are you calling a dog?

119
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,080
Besides,

120
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,679
he's clearly a tough nut to crack.

121
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,120
True.

122
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,120
Such a powerful aura.

123
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:29,399
And here I thought we'd survived.

124
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,240
Don't worry.

125
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,320
I'll collect your bodies.

126
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,360
I'll head out with Tongtong first.

127
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,039
Go.

128
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,679
Fuxi!

129
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,480
Eight Trigrams!

130
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,360
The Imperial Capital isn't a place you can enter

131
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,159
and leave as you please.

132
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,679
Since you're here,

133
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,240
you can all stay for good.

134
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,120
Looks like

135
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,000
we really can't get away this time.

136
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,679
To think the Imperial Capital has a master like this.

137
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,360
I really hadn't heard of him.

138
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,240
Well, Taoists

139
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,559
focus on cultivation.

140
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,519
If they have any money in their pockets,

141
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,960
they won't show their faces.

142
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,279
So it's perfectly normal

143
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,399
that you haven't heard of him.

144
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:23,840
But I wonder about the one in front of us,

145
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,039
what's his deal?

146
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,919
I've got a feeling

147
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,519
this old Taoist

148
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:32,159
is freakishly strong.

149
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,759
So what now?

150
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,080
Give up?

151
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:37,559
Or risk our lives and give it a shot?

152
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,480
Let's give it a shot.

153
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:41,240
We can't just stick our necks out to be slaughtered.

154
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:42,519
That's just too embarrassing.

155
00:10:55,279 --> 00:10:58,600
Your martial arts attainments have reached the grandmaster level.

156
00:10:58,679 --> 00:10:59,600
What a pity.

157
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:00,720
You lack a bit of...

158
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:01,600
intent.

159
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,240
The pressure's so intense!

160
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,080
At your age,

161
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,559
instead of cultivating peacefully in a temple,

162
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:16,200
why pick fights with us youngsters?

163
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,279
It's beneath you.

164
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,240
Just earning my meal ticket.

165
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,519
As for Fuxi's Eight Trigrams art,

166
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,159
I've studied it quite a bit.

167
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:40,080
Set up your formation.

168
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,120
I'm looking forward to it.

169
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,480
I can't beat you.

170
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,600
I'm getting old.

171
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:52,120
Fighting always takes a toll on my body.

172
00:11:52,879 --> 00:11:54,399
The outcome's the same anyway,

173
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:56,240
so let's just skip the

174
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,399
exhausting middle part, shall we?

175
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:14,600
Black Street's got another cripple.

176
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,840
You're not alone anymore.

177
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:23,399
The result should be about the same as if you did it.

178
00:12:23,759 --> 00:12:25,120
His walking days are over.

179
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,840
If you don't believe me,

180
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,200
I can do it again.

181
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,120
No need for that.

182
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:35,519
Anyway, your ultimate fate

183
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:36,919
is death.

184
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,120
For now, as long as you can't move,

185
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,679
that's enough.

186
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,000
This Taoist,

187
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,039
out of everyone I've ever met,

188
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,960
ranks in the top three.

189
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,480
I can hold out for five minutes max.

190
00:12:48,879 --> 00:12:49,600
I'll use my life

191
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,000
to leave him gravely wounded.

192
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,840
If you go crazy,

193
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,320
you'd be the one gravely wounded,

194
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,440
and he'd die.

195
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:57,919
You two could come at me together.

196
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,440
That's fighting dirty.

197
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:01,399
Fighting fair

198
00:13:02,399 --> 00:13:03,399
requires you

199
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,159
to be alive first.

200
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:13,440
Haven't seen anyone this strong in ages.

201
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,600
I want to kill him.

202
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:38,279
You only lasted three seconds?

203
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,559
Which means,

204
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:44,039
if I fought him for half an hour,

205
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,519
that makes me stronger than you

206
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,159
by countless times.

207
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,519
You can't beat me.

208
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,559
Why don't you cripple your own leg,

209
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:56,679
just like old man An,

210
00:13:57,279 --> 00:13:58,559
and skip the middle part?

211
00:13:58,559 --> 00:13:59,159
How about it?

212
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,200
I don't think so.

213
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,720
They'd dock my pay.

214
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:06,840
Besides,

215
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,200
how do you know

216
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,600
I can't beat you?

217
00:14:11,559 --> 00:14:12,240
Fine then.

